               <p>A Second Count for stealing the same goods, the property of the said James.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17841020-84-person832">
                  HANNAH
                   HAWELL
               <interp inst="t17841020-84-person832" type="surname" value="HAWELL"></interp>
