               <p>I live in <placeName id="t17841020-84-crimeloc382">Half-moon-court, Stanhope-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17841020-84-crimeloc382" type="placeName" value="Half-moon-court, Stanhope-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17841020-84-crimeloc382" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17841020-84-off380 t17841020-84-crimeloc382"></join>; my <rs id="t17841020-84-viclabel383" type="occupation">landlord</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17841020-84-victim831 t17841020-84-viclabel383"></join> is Mr. Shepcot; I heard a noise in the lower part of our house, I took a candle and went down stairs, and looked and saw the lead cut up in three junks, and laid on the second stair, I called some neighbours, and a young man and my husband went down stairs, and behind the cellar door they found the prisoner; he said he was disguised in liquor, and went down: I saw the lead found about six o'clock.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17841020-84-person833">
                  WILLIAM
                   WILSON
               <interp inst="t17841020-84-person833" type="surname" value="WILSON"></interp>
